_Nif’al_ Imperative:
The _nif’al_ has an [[{{imperative}} form]] which is one of the [[Nif’al Forms|forms of the nif’al binyan]].
- The _nif’al_ imperative form has [[_nif’al_ Imperative for regular shorushim|conjugations for regular shorushim]].
- The _nif’al_ imperative form has conjugations for irregular shorushim which will be added at a later time.
